item.description:
@Skiire wrote:

HPBarFull.drawAdvancedSprite(spriteDrawX - 28, spriteDraw - 5;//3

required: int,int,int
found: int,int

spriteDrawX - 28
spriteDraw - 5

Those are your only args, you need one more… Either add the missing arg, we won’t even know where to begin (no reference to the tut) or if you’re sure everything is fine edit the paramaters for drawAdvancedSprite (not recommended).
